                    <note xml:lang="en" type="abstract" resp="http://syriaca.org" corresp="http://syriaca.org/persons http://syriaca.org/q http://syriaca.org/saints">Sharbel and his
                        sister <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/1151">Babai</persName> were
                        martyrs of <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/78">Edessa</placeName>.
                        Sharbel had been a pagan priest, but he converted to Christianity. He was
                        martyred under Trajan. Sharbel and Babai were contemporary with the priest
                            <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/1162">Barsamya</persName>.</note>
